&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err-certificate-has-expired/"&gt;ERR_CERT_HAS_EXPIRED&lt;/a&gt; — certificate expired.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err_socket_timeout/"&gt;ERR_SOCKET_TIMEOUT&lt;/a&gt; — socket timed out.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/javascript/err-connection-reset/"&gt;ERR_CONNECTION_RESET&lt;/a&gt; — connection was reset.&lt;/li&gt;
